body:
We are looking for a Technical Support - IBM Software, for one of the leading distributors of IT products on the Romanian market that is providing the safest and easiest way of interaction. Our client, an IBM business partner, provides complex hardware architectures, software solutions, support pre-sales, service configuration, implementation and maintenance.

Responsabilities:

Offering presales technical support for IBM Software solutions, both to the department colleagues, and to business partners (resellers) and their deficiencies;
Being responsible of the installation, configuration and implementation of IBM software solutions both internally and business partners and their customers;
Identifying and preparing tenders with IBM Software solutions that respond best to the deals requirements of applications from the business partners and from published specifications.

Requirements:

University / Bachelor’s Degree in one of the specialized IT field;
Advanced English skills;
Entry-level experience in programming;
Knowledge of operating systems (Windows, Linux);
Knowledge of IT security structure;
Knowledge of IT infrastructure management;
Knowledge of database systems;
Knowledge of IBM Software Solutions;
General Knowledge of programming languages.
